TITLE: allow depending on edges/nodes
DETAILS: Find a way to make edges (or nodes?) depending on allowed nodes (or edges?). Avoid allowing edges without the corresponding nodes.

TITLE: offline biocypher
DETAILS: Allow biocypher to run on previously cached ontologies if there is no connection.

TITLE: helper property extraction
DETAILS: Find an elegant way to allow property extraction from tabular data.

TITLE: simpler class declaration
DETAILS: See if one can allow for simpler types declaration (with metaclass arguments? https://stackoverflow.com/questions/13762231/how-to-pass-arguments-to-the-metaclass-from-the-class-definition ).

TITLE: ontoweaver module
DETAILS: Modularize out the adapter machinery in an 'ontoweaver' module and use it from there.
